  - ground elevation maps

Update 1.1.3:
  - save/restore window docks layout
  - tower viewpoint selection
  - $rwy alias
  - FGMS XPDR mode guess option


=== 1.2 ===

Version 1.2.0 release date: 17/05/2017
Major feature addition: voice instruction recognition
Other notable changes:
  - indicated air speeds
  - FPL match button in strip detail sheet
  - keyboard PTT indicator in status bar
  - configurable solo weather change interval
  - tower view: bank angle in turns
  - runway details in env. information
  - divided table width strip view
  - location first time splash and data check


=== 1.3 ===

Version 1.3.0 release date: 25/06/2017
Major feature addition: FGMS v1.1.2 + new XPDR properties (GND & IAS)
Other notable changes:
  - speech synthesis for pilot read-back in solo
  - approach spacing hints
  - collecting racks for received strips
  - "speed your discretion" instruction
  - radar mode S capability toggle
  - radar GND mode filter toggle
  - FPL link options on unlinked strip detail sheet
  - strip "!!vect/route" toggle option
  - text alias for strip cruise level
  - traffic selection and finer granularity in path conflict anticipation
  - tower view: nose lift-off on departure
  - mark frozen aircraft on teacher radar
  - silenced session start (3-second sound lock)
  - save sound notification selection
  - pretty printing of XML settings

Update 1.3.1:
  - SSR mode capability selection
  - taxiing AI aircraft stop to avoid collisions
  - teacher can create taxiing aircraft
  - initial solo strips linked to radar contacts
  - strip count and more runway details in env. info dialog
  - "!!ident" and individual cheat/comment indicators in radar tags
  - octal XPDR code spin boxes
  - X-plane nav data update (data cycle 201703)

Update 1.3.2:
  - teacher aircraft squat

Update 1.3.3:
  - per-radar GND mode filter

Update 1.3.4:
  - FG aircraft directory setting for internal tower view
  - menu access to X-plane airport gateway
  - X-plane nav data update (data cycle 201708)


=== 1.4 ===

Version 1.4.0 release date: 5/10/2017
Major feature addition: multiple-window workspace and state save
Other notable changes:
  - per-view rack display
  - radar pan & zoom lock
  - ILS/LOC info sourced from data
  - distractor traffic in solo sessions
  - condensed selection info toolbar
  - runway boxes in separate dock
  - radar colours for XPDR ranges
  - auto-link options for identified received strips
  - option to turn off SSR capability
  - option to log measured coordinates to console

Update 1.4.1:
  - compact radar tags
  - quicker startup
  - location-specific radar settings
  - integrated sector file extraction tool
  - separate files for extracted/custom world AD data

Update 1.4.2:
  - TTS library change to pyttsx3

Update 1.4.3:
  - text radio history time limit and clear option
  - OpenRadar handover range setting
  - abort mouse instructions with RMB


